  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/11340dea79dd76fd2e51d732d75d4b1f.avif?t=1689581337\" width=616 height=99 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Pocket Planet?</h2>Do you want to build beautiful worlds without investing hours on end in stressful resource management? Say no more! Pocket Planet should be right up your alley.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/18edbc98bf5d88fa8d3e34c1af37c127.poster.avif?t=1689581337\" width=616 height=411 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/18edbc98bf5d88fa8d3e34c1af37c127.webm?t=1689581337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Pocket Planet is a minimalist puzzle game about building dioramas on a hexagonal grid. Explore a large number of ever-changing new worlds featuring different biomes and enjoy the relaxing atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/d5e00b4bd85ceb102a7c293834b8307e.avif?t=1689581337\" width=616 height=99 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game offers you:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Intuitive and rewarding diorama-building gameplay </li><li> More than 200 levels divided into several worlds </li><li> Different biomes featuring different placement mechanics and combinations </li><li> A relaxing atmosphere </li><li> Beautiful, vibrant colors </li><li>Great for playing every now and then, discovering some new worlds and completing all the quests </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pocket Planet is inspired by amazing games like</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dorfromantik </li><li> Townscaper </li><li> Valley Between </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/11340dea79dd76fd2e51d732d75d4b1f.avif?t=1689581337\" width=616 height=99 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Pocket Planet?</h2>Do you want to build beautiful worlds without investing hours on end in stressful resource management? Say no more! Pocket Planet should be right up your alley.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/18edbc98bf5d88fa8d3e34c1af37c127.poster.avif?t=1689581337\" width=616 height=411 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/18edbc98bf5d88fa8d3e34c1af37c127.webm?t=1689581337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Pocket Planet is a minimalist puzzle game about building dioramas on a hexagonal grid. Explore a large number of ever-changing new worlds featuring different biomes and enjoy the relaxing atmosphere.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197980/extras/d5e00b4bd85ceb102a7c293834b8307e.avif?t=1689581337\" width=616 height=99 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game offers you:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Intuitive and rewarding diorama-building gameplay </li><li> More than 200 levels divided into several worlds </li><li> Different biomes featuring different placement mechanics and combinations </li><li> A relaxing atmosphere </li><li> Beautiful, vibrant colors </li><li>Great for playing every now and then, discovering some new worlds and completing all the quests </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pocket Planet is inspired by amazing games like</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dorfromantik </li><li> Townscaper </li><li> Valley Between </li></ul>",
